# Anthropic API key — get one at https://console.anthropic.com/
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the real value there.
#
# Secrets policy (see docs/vision/security.md):
# - Real values live only in .env.local (gitignored, never committed).
# - This file (.env.example) is committed and contains placeholders only.
# - Never log this value.
# - Never expose it to client-side code (no NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix).
# - Only a Next.js Route Handler may read this and call the Anthropic SDK.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
